REDUX FORM

It will help us to validate any field typed by user and will make us able to use the content of these fields into any other forms.

https://redux-form.com

Install

	It must be installed into the client side. 
	So go to your client directory and type:

		$ npm install --save redux-form

Documentation

	https://redux-form.com/7.4.2/docs/gettingstarted.md/